# Code owners for automated review requests
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo
# Replace with your GitHub username or team
* @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Airflow Intelligence Agent
/agents/airflow_intelligence/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# CI/CD and workflows
/.github/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Documentation
*.md @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/docs/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/agents/*/docs/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Deployment configurations
/agents/*/deploy/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
**/Dockerfile @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
**/docker-compose*.yml @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
**/kubernetes/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Security-sensitive files
.env.template @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
**/requirements*.txt @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/.github/workflows/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME

# Tests
/tests/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
/agents/*/tests/ @YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME
